Titolo: Fuzion Frenzy

Anno: 2001

Descrizione: Fuzion Frenzy is a launch title for the Microsoft Xbox. At its core, Fuzion Frenzy is a four-player party game featuring 45 different mini-games (not including the titular Fuzion Frenzy). A demo of the game was included with some other launch titles in the U.S., including Halo, Munch's Oddysee, Project Gotham Racing and Amped.
A sequel was later released for the Xbox 360, entitled Fuzion Frenzy 2.

Genere: Party 

Valutazione: 59
